Installation:
Pull the project from git to a local folder: https://github.com/Dandusshh/FinalQAProject.git
Open the project in PyCharm

or Open PyCharm and open a project from VCS https://github.com/Dandusshh/FinalQAProject.git

If required need to create a new environment (venv). On windows: py -m venv venv
Activate venv: .\venv\Scripts\activate
If error of powershell that script is "not digitally signed" then run: Set-ExecutionPolicy -Scope Process -ExecutionPolicy Bypass

Install dependencies: pip install -r 'requirements.txt'

If PyCharm requires to configure python interpreter then click on the gear and select the existing environment "venv"

Running:
To run selenium tests select the test_selenium.py, right click on it and select Run python tests. Expected 2 success 1 fail
To run api tests select the test_api.py, right click on it and select Run python tests. Expected 2 success

To run all the tests together right click the project name and select "Run Python tests..."